          "date": "2015-11-02 11:15:11.000000000",
          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-6612 obdfilter: do not overwrite OBD_MD_FLCOOKIE flag",
        "message": "LU-6612 obdfilter: do not overwrite OBD_MD_FLCOOKIE flag\n\nA (long standing!) bug has been introduced (by commit d2d56f38)\ncausing OBD_MD_FLCOOKIE flag to be unset in both callbacks\nhandling Unlink and Setattr LLOG records during MDS/OSTs\nreplay/recovery process.\nThis is causing these records to never be canceled and removed\nfrom LLOGs (and likely to be unnecessarily be re-processed each\ntime), leading to concerned plain LLOGs to be kept on MDS.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3d2180214018899fe089f02ce400a0c4134dd8e1\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
  },
